Trinity::

She went running down the hall, turned left and headed for the engine 
room.  She found a corner under a small A/C unit and curled up under 
it.  She cried,"I don't want to lose any more.....I lost Mom and Dad 
in the crash...I don't want to lose...lose.." as she cried her optics 
out. "IT'S NOT FAIR!!!!"
